  "remarks": "KAA is an IRGC-owned company involved in large scale civil and military\nconstruction projects and other engineering activities. It undertakes a significant\namount of work on Passive Defense Organization projects. In particular, KAA subsidiaries\nwere heavily involved in the construction of the uranium enrichment site at Qom/Fordow.\n[Old Reference # E.29.II.7]",
